resources.string: OnePlus has been a really quite, but still classy brand. Their new flagship, Oneplus 9 really offers something different compared to the other brand. Despite having a flagship specification in every way possible, the price they offer is only half of almost all the other flagship available.
Fluid AMOLED, 120Hz, HDR10+, 1100 nits (peak)\n Corning Gorilla Glass 5\n Always-on display
6.55 inches, 103.6 cm2 (~87.6% screen-to-body ratio)\n 1080 x 2400 pixels, 20:9 ratio (~402 ppi density)

Li-Po 4500 mAh, non-removable
 65W wired, PD, 1-100% in 29 min (advertised)
 15W wireless (EU/NA)
